<section id="opensource">
  <h2>Open Source</h2>

  <article class="project">
    <h3><a href="https://github.com/django-guardian/django-guardian/pull/838">django-guardian — bug fix (merged upstream)</a></h3>
    <p>Discovered a crash in <code>get_groups_with_perms</code> when using custom group
    permission models, made it reproducible with a test case, and contributed the fix —
    merged into the official repository of Django's object-level permissions library.</p>
    <p class="meta">Python · Django</p>
  </article>

  <article class="project">
    <h3><a href="https://github.com/BonaFideIT/django-otplink">django-otplink</a></h3>
    <p>A Django module of my own that generates expiring one-time or multi-use links for
    files in Django models and storage — for instance protected downloads that
    automatically become invalid after expiry or use.</p>
    <p class="meta">Python · Django</p>
  </article>

  <article class="project">
    <h3><a href="https://github.com/okaluk/StudyDrive-Downloader-Extension">StudyDrive Downloader Extension</a></h3>
    <p>Chrome extension for downloading StudyDrive documents — adopted as a fork and
    independently maintained and extended.</p>
    <p class="meta">JavaScript · Chrome Extension</p>
  </article>
